<section id="inline">
  <title>DMLex Inline Markup Module</title>
  <para>This module makes it possible to mark up substrings inside the string values of certain
    objects and to attach properties to them.</para>
  <para>It is up to the implementer to decide how to implement inline markup in an implementation of
    the DMLex Inline Markup module, whether <emphasis>in-place</emphasis> (as XML) or as
      <emphasis>stand-off</emphasis> markup (for example through start and end indexes).</para>
